TopicTitle: [Looking for a mod] Soviet N1 Rocket Engine

Articles.Content:
Hello.

I love the multi-nozzle design of the N1 soviet rockets engines. Where can I find their models, even if not updated to 1.0.4?

I know of BobCat's Proton and N1 rocket part packs, but the N1 rocket engines there are integrated with the fuel tanks and are not available separately.

You might try DennyTX it will need alittle update [http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/79797-N-1-Soviet-Heavy-Booster-%28OLDD-in-USSR%29-v-0-235-%2813-05-14%29?p=1154077&viewfull=1#post1154077](https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/79797-N-1-Soviet-Heavy-Booster-%28OLDD-in-USSR%29-v-0-235-%2813-05-14%29?p=1154077&viewfull=1#post1154077)

EDIT- And also think NovaPunch has one [http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/3870](https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/3870)
